{
  "stem": "2316.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he got permission to go back on the [NON-ENGLISH] to be with his wife and children.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's how I found my dad and brought him-- I didn't bring him back, but he came back afterwards.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was just a kid.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know, you know?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Kiev was three million people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I'm tramping around looking for Eli Potash.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, come on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I wouldn't even do it now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it's easier now.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But that was-- you know, so many miracles happened.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You-- you just can't figure it out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You can't even begin to understand why and what.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There's not-- nothing makes any sense, really and truly.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And months later, my dad joined us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And eventually, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we-- there was a time-- we still lived at the [NON-ENGLISH] until there was a time when the war was almost over.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It must have been almost over, or over, maybe.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they passed a law that any Polish people, citizens, can go back to Poland if they want.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my dad, my mother, and my brother, came back to-- there was no shtetl to come back to, because, as the last time we left the shtetl, it was burned to the ground.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were in the woods watching burn our house and everybody else's homes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All the homes were burned to the ground that night when we ran away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Was this right at the beginning?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was like the second time, the second ghetto, the second time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They burnt every house, because they were all wooden houses.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They burnt every single house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You don't know-- there's wilderness right there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You can't-- you don't know if there was a shtetl there at all.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the Nazis burned it down to the ground.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
